{
  "stem": "24470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called a Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it had, uh, classes from first grade to sixth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- I started from first grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- spoken language was Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were taught Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of, uh, Tanakh in-- in-- not in Hebrew, in Polish-- stories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, it's the Bible, the Old Testament, the Bible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember starting Latin in the sixth grade, beginning of sixth-- actually, in fifth grade, we started.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Hebrew was taught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "English, I studied privately, just before the break of the war a little bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a normal life of a normal childhood until '39.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- my mother's relative lived in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother's youngest sister was a very pretty-- she was 11 years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I was 12, it made her 23?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, she was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had her picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember in school, the girls, we collected pictures of artists, of actors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the girls, my friends in school, want-- thought that she's an actress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they wanted to exchange pictures with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That aunt of mine, when we used to come to Warsaw, she introduced me to opera.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was-- the first time when I was 12, I saw in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it made a tremendous impression on me, especially, I remember, as today, the garden where Marguerite is meeting with Faust.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember-- Faust-- with Faust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember Mephistopheles coming out from the flames on the floor of the stage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I guess I was so impressed that from then on, I was always interested in oper-- in opera.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm an opera lover even now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some memories from childhood that remain with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather and grandmother, I remember vaguely.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
